    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>to a small bowl with your <strong>miso</strong>, <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>mirin</strong> (you'll use the rest for later!), <strong>shichimi togarashi </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and a squeeze of <strong>lime juice</strong> (save most of it for later!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>miso marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1620225585651-x200.jpg",
