        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>salmon fillet[s]</strong> into 6 bite-sized pieces per person</p><p>Add the <strong>salmon pieces</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>miso marinade</strong> (save the rest for later!) and gently mix until all of the salmon is coated and set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
