        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> cucumber </strong>in half lengthways and finely dice</p><p>Slice your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone[s] and remove the stone[s] using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin and chop into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped avocado</strong> and <strong>diced</strong> <strong>cucumber</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> </strong>juice<strong> </strong>of the<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>remaining lime[s] </strong>and your <strong>sesame seeds </strong>– this is your <strong>sesame avo salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
