    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong> into 6 batons per person</p><p>Thread each <strong>skewer</strong> with <strong>3 marinated salmon pieces</strong> and <strong>3 spring onion batons </strong>– these are your <strong>miso</strong> <strong>salmon skewers</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick), with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1620225658670-x200.jpg",
